### Benjamin's Ultimate Loan Test with Time-Travel & Penalty Tracking
### Uses existing Benjamin (BVL-2022-000001) - Tests all 104 installments
### Location: backend/benjamin-ultimate-test-with-timetravel.http

### ==================== 1. LOGIN ====================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "jaytechwavesolutions@gmail.com",
  "password": "Michira._2000"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("csrf_token", response.body.user.id);
  // Benjamin already exists - just use his member number
  client.global.set("member_number", "BVL-2022-000001");
%}

### ==================== 3. CONFIGURE TIME-TRAVELER ====================
### Start: Oct 6, 2022 | End: Aug 28, 2025
### 7 days per tick = Benjamin's entire 3-year cycle

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/time-travel/configure
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{sacco_cookie}}
X-XSRF-TOKEN: {{csrf_token}}

{
  "startDate": "2022-10-06",
  "endDate": "2025-08-28",
  "daysPerTick": 7
}

### ==================== 4. DISBURSE LOAN 1 (Oct 6, 2022) ====================

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/migration/loans/disburse
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{sacco_cookie}}
X-XSRF-TOKEN: {{csrf_token}}

{
  "memberNumber": "{{member_number}}",
  "loanProductCode": "Historical Smart Loan",
  "principal": 1000000.00,
  "interestRate": 20,
  "termWeeks": 104,
  "disbursementDate": "2022-10-06",
  "referenceNumber": "LOAN-BENJAMIN-001"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("loan1_id", response.body.id);
%}


### ==================== 5. VERIFY INITIAL SCHEDULE ====================

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/loans/schedule?memberNumber={{member_number}}

---

### ==================== 6. CHECK INITIAL STATE (Day 0) ====================

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/time-travel/status

---

### ==================== 7. ADVANCE WEEK 1 (Oct 13, 2022) - INSTALLMENT DUE ====================

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/time-travel/advance?days=7
Cookie: {{sacco_cookie}}
X-XSRF-TOKEN: {{csrf_token}}

---

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/time-travel/status

---

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/loans/schedule?memberNumber={{member_number}}&weekNumber=1

---

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/penalties?memberNumber={{member_number}}

---

### ==================== 8. ADVANCE WEEK 8 (Nov 24, 2022) - FIRST PENALTY TRIGGERS ====================

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/time-travel/advance?days=49
Cookie: {{sacco_cookie}}
X-XSRF-TOKEN: {{csrf_token}}

---

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/time-travel/status

---

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/loans/schedule?memberNumber={{member_number}}&weekNumber=1

---

GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/penalties?memberNumber={{member_number}}
# Expected: 20% penalty on week 1 installment

---

